Definition: a serious chronic and progressive inflammation of the ileum producing frequent bouts of diarrhea with abdominal pain and nausea and fever and weight loss
Synonyms: regional_ileitis, Crohn, s_disease, colitis, a, serious, chronic, and, progressive, inflammation, of, the, ileum, producing, frequent, bouts, diarrhea, with, abdominal, pain, nausea, fever, weight, loss
Category: noun.state
